dreisoft.tresos.datamodel2.api.model.expr

Class MOr

  • java.lang.Object
    • dreisoft.tresos.datamodel2.api.model.expr.MOr
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMExpr

    public class MOr
extends java.lang.Object
implements IMExpr
    Returns the union set of all contexts returned by all given expression. E.g.: 
     ctxt.getAll(new MOr(new MChild(), new MParent()));
    returns all children and the parent context.
